 \"from\": 1345, \"to\": 1363}, {\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 1367, \"to\": 1373}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1415, \"to\": 1427}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1442}, {\"ngram\": \"another one\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1480}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Olympics in London, the finals day, when we played the singles and the mixed final was definitely one of the one of the best days of my professional life.\", \"from\": 1508, \"to\": 1667, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1531, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.8055958407464152, \"rank\": 0.24129206580807266, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1521}, {\"ngram\": \"the finals day\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"the singles\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1575}, {\"ngram\": \"the mixed final\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1595}, {\"ngram\": \"the best days\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"my professional life\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Definitely one of the happiest I have felt more so than when I won Wimbledon in 2013 or even the US Open.\", \"from\": 1669, \"to\": 1775, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wimbledon\", \"from\": 1737, \"to\": 1746}, {\"ngram\": \"even the US Open\", \"from\": 1758, \"to\": 1774}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was just an amazing experience, to be part of an Olympic team.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1843, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"just an amazing experience\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1811}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1819, \"to\": 1823}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic team\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am a massive, massive sports fan.\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1879, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a massive, massive sports fan\", \"from\": 1849, \"to\": 1878}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have always enjoyed team competitions, probably more than individual competitions, whether that be as a junior or playing in Davis Cup or Olympics.\", \"from\": 1880, \"to\": 2029, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2007, \"end\": 2016, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davis_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.6468090286933198e-12, \"text\": \"Davis Cup\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davis_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Davis_Cup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"team competitions\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1919}, {\"ngram\": \"individual competitions\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1963}, {\"ngram\": \"a junior\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 1992}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympics\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2028}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I have loved it.\\\"\", \"from\": 2030, \"to\": 2047, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As much as Murray has excelled on the Olympic stage - becoming the only person to have won multiple singles gold medals, there have also been setbacks.\", \"from\": 2049, \"to\": 2200, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2060, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2265155952629146e-38, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic stage\", \"from\": 2083, \"to\": 2100}, {\"ngram\": \"the only person\", \"from\": 2112, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple singles gold medals\", \"from\": 2140, \"to\": 2168}, {\"ngram\": \"setbacks\", \"from\": 2191, \"to\": 2199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2008, he suffered a shock defeat to Lu Yen-Hsun, of Chinese Taipei, in the first round, while three years 