ence\", \"from\": 2722, \"to\": 2740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Total almost full body cramp in the first round there and a really tough, tough loss for me.\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"almost full body cramp\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"the first round\", \"from\": 2780, \"to\": 2795}, {\"ngram\": \"a really tough, tough loss\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And last Olympics, me and Joe were up a set and a break in the quarter-finals.\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2921, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2869, \"end\": 2872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"score\": 0.9563582447640091, \"rank\": 0.04549409799403521, \"text\": \"Joe\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Joe_DiMaggio\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"last Olympics\", \"from\": 2847, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"a break\", \"from\": 2891, \"to\": 2898}, {\"ngram\": \"the quarter-finals\", \"from\": 2902, \"to\": 2920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had game points, 4-3 in the second set and got broken.\", \"from\": 2922, \"to\": 2979, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"game points\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2940}, {\"ngram\": \"the second set\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2963}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We would have had a couple of matches to win a medal there and that was a tough loss so I have had some great moments but also some difficult ones in the Olympics, but always amazing experience, and I have learned a lot from them.\\\"\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 3211, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a couple\", \"from\": 2998, \"to\": 3006}, {\"ngram\": \"matches\", \"from\": 3010, \"to\": 3017}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 3025, \"to\": 3032}, {\"ngram\": \"a tough loss\", \"from\": 3052, \"to\": 3064}, {\"ngram\": \"some great moments\", \"from\": 3079, \"to\": 3097}, {\"ngram\": \"some difficult ones\", \"from\": 3107, \"to\": 3126}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 3130, \"to\": 3142}, {\"ngram\": \"always amazing experience\", \"from\": 3148, \"to\": 3173}, {\"ngram\": \"a lot\", \"from\": 3194, \"to\": 3199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Part of Murray's doubt over his participation is struggles with his back on clay court in recent times.\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3316, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3221, \"end\": 3227, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.2265155952629146e-38, \"text\": \"Murray\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andy_Murray\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Part\", \"from\": 3213, \"to\": 3217}, {\"ngram\": \"his participation\", \"from\": 3241, \"to\": 3258}, {\"ngram\": \"struggles\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3271}, {\"ngram\": \"his back\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"clay court\", \"from\": 3289, \"to\": 3299}, {\"ngram\": \"recent times\", \"from\": 3303, \"to\": 3315}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That dates back to an operation he underwent on his back all the way back in 2013.\", \"from\": 3317, \"to\": 3399, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an operation\", \"from\": 3336, \"to\": 3348}, {\"ngram\": \"his back\", \"from\": 3365, \"to\": 3373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By contrast, the grass courts of the Queen's Club, on which he is competing this week at a venue where he has won a record five titles, do not affect him.\", \"from\": 3401, \"to\": 3555, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contrast\", \"from\": 3404, \"to\": 3412}, {\"ngram\": \"the grass courts\", \"from\": 3414, \"to\": 3430}, {\"ngram\": \"the Queen's Club\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3450}, {\"ngram\": \"a venue\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3497}, {\"ngram\": \"a record five titles\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On cla